  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will bring about social and behaviour change to improve normative behaviours around face washing and environmental sanitation in Uganda. This contributes to a combined strategic and nationally coordinated communication response to prevent trachoma in Uganda, by:
&#x2022; Development of an e-toolkit for the &#x2018;Facial cleanliness&#x2019; and &#x2018;Environmental change&#x2019; components of trachoma prevention, based on the findings of the situation analysis and formative research
&#x2022; Production of a physical toolkit of communication materials promoting Facial cleanliness and Environmental change to prevent trachoma.</narrative>
  </description>
